<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الاِسْتِغَاثَةِ مَعَ قُوَّةِ السُّلْطَانِ وَحُضُورِهِ فَالأَْصَحُّ أَنَّهُمْ قُطَّاعٌ وَبِهِ قَطَعَ الْقَفَّال وَالْبَغَوِيُّ <span class="c2">(١)</span> ، وَمَذْهَبُ الْحَنَابِلَةِ كَمَذْهَبِ الشَّافِعِيَّةِ فِي الْجُمْلَةِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مُكَاتَبٌ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">انْظُرْ:</span> مُكَاتَبَةٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
